    "en": {
      "title": "There is no electricity for three hours even on weekends",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Public Utilities Commission said today (26) afternoon that the current 3-hour power cut will be implemented tomorrow and the day after (27 and 28). Due to the sudden collapse of the Lakwijaya Coal Plant in Norochchole and lack of fuel for power generation, this further power cut is maintained for a period of three hours.",
        "Accordingly, the Public Utilities Commission stated that electricity will be cut for 20 hours and 40 minutes during the day and 20 hours and 20 minutes during the night from 'A' to 'W'."
      ],
      "title_ents": [
        {
          "text": "three hours",
          "label": "TIME"
        }
      ],
